---
---

<header class="bg-white border-b border-slate-100 py-16 md:py-24 px-4 overflow-hidden relative">
    <!-- Abstract background elements -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mr-20 -mt-20 w-80 h-80 bg-blue-50 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-50"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 -ml-20 -mb-20 w-80 h-80 bg-indigo-50 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-50"></div>

    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center relative">
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-8">
            <img src="/logo.png" alt="Caribe Suite Logo" class="h-24 w-auto drop-shadow-sm" />
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-slate-900 text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold mb-6 tracking-tight">
            🌴 Caribe Suite
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-600 mb-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
            La plataforma integral para gestionar tu negocio con facilidad y eficiencia.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-500 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Un sistema de gestión empresarial diseñado para simplificar la administración de tu empresa. Con una interfaz moderna y accesible desde cualquier dispositivo.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
            <a href="#features" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-blue-200 active:scale-95">
                Ver módulos destacados
            </a>
            <a href="#about" class="bg-white text-slate-700 border border-slate-200 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-slate-50 transition-all active:scale-95">
                Conocer más
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-16 flex items-center justify-center gap-8 text-slate-400">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-700">100%</span>
                <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">Cloud Ready</span>
            </div>
            <div class="h-8 w-px bg-slate-200"></div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-700">Multi</span>
                <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">Dispositivo</span>
            </div>
            <div class="h-8 w-px bg-slate-200"></div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-700">Real-time</span>
                <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">Sincronización</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</header>
